text: “You can work and work and work on something, and bang your head against the wall and know it inside and out — but then,” said Jesse Plemons, the lead in the new Charlie Kaufman film, “if you’re not relaxed in your mind and body, that’s all for nothing.” https://t.co/V5XINc3TNF
